│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // This file implements the SLP vectorizer. It detects consecutive memory                                                                                                                │
│ // accesses that can be grouped into vector operations. This optimization                                                                                                                │
│ // is complementing the loop vectorizer and can be used in cases where the                                                                                                               │
│ // loop vectorizer fails.                                                                                                                                                                │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ // The implementation is based on the paper:                                                                                                                                             │
│ //  "Loop-Aware SLP in GCC" by Ira Rosen, Dorit Nuzman, and Ayal Zaks.                                                                                                                   │
│ //  http://www.cs.tau.ac.il/~dorit/papers/cgo07.pdf                                                                                                                                      │
│ //                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ //===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//                                                                                                         │
